            note="
                !+AgendaItem_group(mr, dec-2012) am exposing the group field to
                UI but making it modifiable only by Admin (but visible by everyone).
                
                The intention of the logic (currently an application-side assumption)
                for AgendaItems is that they are ALWAYS created in a committee context
                and that committee is what is automatically set as the group.
                
